## 6. FILE UPLOAD SECURITY — 🚨 CRITICAL

### 🔴 Issue 6.1: No File Type Validation — Arbitrary File Upload

- **Severity:** **CRITICAL**
- **Issue:** The `uploadFile` function in [content.ts#L162-L221](file:///c:/Users/habib/Downloads/admin-panel-plan-2/app/admin/actions/content.ts#L162-L221) accepts **any file** — there is zero validation of:
  - File extension (`.html`, `.php`, `.svg`, `.exe` all accepted)
  - MIME type (the `file.type` is passed to Supabase but not validated)
  - File content (no magic byte checking)
- **Impact:** Combined with Issue 2.1 (no auth on upload), anyone can upload:
  - HTML files with JavaScript (XSS via direct URL access)
  - SVG files with embedded scripts
  - Server-side scripts (if local fallback is used in certain hosting)
  - Malware or illegal content
- **Location:** [content.ts#L162-L221](file:///c:/Users/habib/Downloads/admin-panel-plan-2/app/admin/actions/content.ts#L162-L221)
- **Fix:**
```ts
const ALLOWED_EXTENSIONS = ['.jpg', '.jpeg', '.png', '.gif', '.webp', '.svg', '.pdf']
const ALLOWED_MIME_TYPES = [
  'image/jpeg', 'image/png', 'image/gif', 'image/webp', 'image/svg+xml', 'application/pdf'
]
const MAX_FILE_SIZE = 5 * 1024 * 1024 // 5MB

export async function uploadFile(formData: FormData) {
  await requireAdmin() // Fix Issue 2.1 first
  
  const file = formData.get('file') as File | null
  if (!file) return { error: 'No file provided' }
  
  // Validate file size
  if (file.size > MAX_FILE_SIZE) return { error: 'File too large (max 5MB)' }
  
  // Validate extension
  const ext = path.extname(file.name).toLowerCase()
  if (!ALLOWED_EXTENSIONS.includes(ext)) {
    return { error: `File type not allowed: ${ext}` }
  }
  
  // Validate MIME type
  if (!ALLOWED_MIME_TYPES.includes(file.type)) {
    return { error: `MIME type not allowed: ${file.type}` }
  }
  
  // For SVGs, additional sanitization is needed
  if (ext === '.svg') {
    const text = await file.text()
    if (text.includes('<script') || text.includes('javascript:') || text.includes('on')) {
      return { error: 'SVG contains potentially unsafe content' }
    }
  }
  // ... proceed
}
```

