- **Severity:** Medium
- **Issue:** Neither `next.config.mjs` nor `netlify.toml` configure security headers. Missing headers include:
  - `Content-Security-Policy` (CSP)
  - `Strict-Transport-Security` (HSTS)
  - `X-Frame-Options`
  - `X-Content-Type-Options`
  - `Referrer-Policy`
  - `Permissions-Policy`
- **Location:** [next.config.mjs](file:///c:/Users/habib/Downloads/admin-panel-plan-2/next.config.mjs), [netlify.toml](file:///c:/Users/habib/Downloads/admin-panel-plan-2/netlify.toml)
- **Fix:** Add to `next.config.mjs`:
```js
const nextConfig = {
  // ... existing config
  async headers() {
    return [
      {
